Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.16,0:00:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Previously on "Transformers Prime"...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.36,0:00:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shockwave... I thought you'd perished on Cybertron.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.36,0:00:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The patch failed to yield any new information on the whereabouts of the Autobots.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.56,0:00:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I' d know the hum of that engine anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.96,0:00:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jackie!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.26,0:00:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't just give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.56,0:00:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then tell me what we can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.46,0:00:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We know Starscream had access to a groundbridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.66,0:00:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'd clearly been using the Harbinger.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.16,0:00:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It could be full of Cybertronian tech.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.66,0:00:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Resources won't be of much use,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.36,0:00:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,not without someone to lead us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.26,0:00:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Forge.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.16,0:00:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you had the Forge, you could fix yourself up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.06,0:00:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meet Ultra Magnus.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.06,0:00:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I present to you, my liege,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.96,0:00:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the ultimate Autobot hunter.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.26,0:01:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Predacon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.06,0:01:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've been extinct since the beginning of Cybertronian history.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.66,0:01:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.36,0:01:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the specimen you see before you was bred in the laboratory,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.46,0:01:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,cloned from fossilized remains, which I discovered on Cybertron.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.06,0:01:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shockwave, it does my spark good to see you once again tampering with creation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.76,0:01:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master, please! Keep your distance!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.16,0:01:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No need for alarm. The beast is completely under my control.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.46,0:01:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such primal magnificence.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.36,0:02:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A sample of Energon, from Wheeljack, spilled during the Autobot's failed interrogation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.16,0:02:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let the hunt begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.96,0:03:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys, you know I'm all for blowin' the scrap outta stuff,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.26,0:03:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,280)}but what does flattening a Decepticon mine have to do with getting the band back together and taking down Megatron?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.16,0:03:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,280)}Simple. When we light up this place, the blast'll be big and unmistakable.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.36,0:03:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,280)}Any Autobot within 500 klicks will see the sky glowin' with Energon, and come runnin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.16,0:03:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then bring the rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.96,0:03:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,280)}Mainframe's up and running.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.06,0:03:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,280)}But I'll need help hacking the operating codes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.76,0:03:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,280)}Even if the groundbridge proves functional,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.96,0:03:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,280)}it will be next to worthless without a means of pinpointing the current locations of our compatriots.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.56,0:03:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Use your head, Bumblebee.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.06,0:03:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the Decepticons had the ability to track Autobot signals,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.96,0:04:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'd have all been at Megatron's mercy here on Earth a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.76,0:04:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... Back where we started.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.56,0:04:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But not if I can reconfigure these Decepticon frequencies.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.06,0:04:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the very least, we may be able to access their comm-link.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.06,0:04:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one's seen or heard from you since Cybertron went dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.26,0:04:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you find your way to Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.86,0:04:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soldier, we may not be on Cybertron,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.56,0:04:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but military protocol remains.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.06,0:04:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My apologies, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.76,0:04:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.26,0:04:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Advise the native life-form to watch its tone as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.56,0:04:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Who is this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.26,0:04:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ultra Magnus was Optimus' key Lieutenant during the war back on Cybertron.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.16,0:04:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very "by the book". Just go with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.86,0:04:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As for your broader question,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.46,0:04:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my story is that of all Autobots since the exodus.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.06,0:04:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wandered the spaceways in search of others,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.16,0:04:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,reuniting with some,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.06,0:05:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,often only to see them fall at the hands of the Decepticons.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.96,0:05:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until you detected the Omega beam, and followed it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.66,0:05:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you are referring to the massive energy burst originating from Cybertron,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.86,0:05:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that would be affirmative.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.16,0:05:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Upon my arrival, it became evident that this planet had been invaded.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.36,0:05:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My scanners also detected Autobot life signals,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.36,0:05:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,yours being in closest proximity to my position.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.46,0:05:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Signals? As in plural?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.96,0:05:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.56,0:05:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Five total.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.96,0:05:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.56,0:05:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jack, that doesn't necessarily mean what you're thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.76,0:05:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Autobot signals can't be detected when they're shielded.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.66,0:05:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cozy little place you built for yourself, Megatron.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.06,0:05:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finding the Forge in there may take awhile.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.16,0:05:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, again,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.46,0:05:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,maybe you still keep your valuables in the usual place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.76,0:06:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you down, Optimus.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.46,0:06:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, "overreacting?"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.76,0:06:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Easy for you to say, Knockout.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.56,0:06:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody here wants your post.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.16,0:06:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, on the other hand, hold the most coveted position within the Decepticon ranks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.16,0:06:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And no matter what he may claim,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.36,0:06:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that Shockwave is plotting to usurp me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.86,0:06:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see the smug look in his eye
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.96,0:06:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when he unveiled that vile beast to lord Megatron?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.96,0:07:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't scare me, ugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.66,0:07:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.46,0:07:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Munitions planted.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.06,0:07:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get this party started.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.96,0:07:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Company.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.96,0:07:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Megatron?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.36,0:07:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah. Bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.86,0:07:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I don't remember seeing that move in buckethead's repertoire.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.06,0:08:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.36,0:08:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd the 'Cons get a dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.76,0:08:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- What's a dragon?\N- What's a dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.36,0:08:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Giant flying fire-breathing lizard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.16,0:08:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bulkhead, you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.86,0:09:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Easy, I may be hot to the touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.86,0:09:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why isn't it coming after us?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.96,0:09:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lookin' for me, beast?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.96,0:09:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.16,0:09:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna need more firepower!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.16,0:09:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good thing I know just where to find some!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.86,0:09:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Incoming!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.76,0:09:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Autobots!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.16,0:10:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the walls came tumblin' down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.36,0:10:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Snuff the tragic dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.06,0:10:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're toast.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.56,0:10:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of ours?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.66,0:10:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.56,0:11:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Jack!\N- Arcee!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.36,0:11:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miko. Can't breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.06,0:11:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weakling.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.66,0:11:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the save.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.06,0:11:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank the Commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.76,0:11:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.36,0:11:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.46,0:11:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ultra Magnus? It's an honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.76,0:11:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an honor, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.46,0:11:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess blowin' that mine made us pretty easy to spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.36,0:12:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ultra Magnus already had a bead on your signals,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.36,0:12:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.66,0:12:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Care to tell us what exactly's nipping at our tailpipes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.46,0:12:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We think it's a robot dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.06,0:12:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or a Cybertronian reptile.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.66,0:12:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brace yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.56,0:13:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's right on top of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.76,0:14:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it now, lord Megatron?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.66,0:14:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agent Fowler, it's Ratchet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.16,0:14:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ratchet? Where's Jack? Is he with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.66,0:14:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, he is not.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.66,0:14:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, we don't have much time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.46,0:15:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have taken a tremendous, yet calculated, risk in contacting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.26,0:15:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hopefully, the Decepticons are not monitoring their own frequencies as closely as they no doubt are those of the humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.56,0:15:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am transmitting our current coordinates.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.26,0:15:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.16,0:15:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ratchet, have you heard from anyone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.76,0:15:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Prime?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.46,0:15:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's one of ours!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.56,0:15:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raf!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.86,0:16:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Girl's got a grip, doesn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.26,0:16:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.86,0:16:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ultra Magnus?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.76,0:16:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.76,0:16:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a grave disappointment this must be for you, master.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.76,0:16:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And to make matters worse,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.66,0:16:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because it cannot speak, we have no way of knowing why the Predacon failed so miserably.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.46,0:16:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Poor, mute, mindless creature.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.66,0:16:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,New paint job looks good, Bee.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.66,0:16:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least you had something to work with.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.36,0:16:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I reversed my colors, I'd be pink.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.16,0:16:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The communications link needs further calibration to be compatible with Autobot frequencies.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.36,0:16:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The groundbridge, however, is fully operational.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.46,0:17:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That would've come in handy when robo-dragon was trying to eat us for breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.06,0:17:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The indigenous population of this planet, do they all display the same disregard for authority?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.66,0:17:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. Mostly just Miko.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.16,0:17:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Don't shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.06,0:17:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Fowler. He's with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.96,0:17:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, mom. I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.56,0:17:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your families are safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.26,0:17:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agent Fowler saw to it that Jasper was evacuated in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.76,0:17:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only signals Ultra Magnus was able to isolate are standing right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.26,0:17:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe his scanner's faulty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.66,0:17:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the kid's unaccounted for.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.66,0:18:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smokescreen bridged out unaccompanied.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.86,0:18:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only Optimus knows where.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.46,0:18:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Optimus remained behind,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.36,0:18:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to destroy the groundbridge, to ensure that everyone else... made it to safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.66,0:18:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I watched the base go down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.46,0:18:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one or thing walked out of there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.36,0:18:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not that we could see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.66,0:18:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if Prime survived,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.56,0:18:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure we can afford to wait for him to show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.96,0:18:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not with Megatron holding our planet hostage
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.36,0:18:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from his high and mighty perch at Darkmount.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.36,0:18:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would be inclined to agree with the native life-form.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.66,0:18:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must stop Megatron,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.56,0:18:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with or without Optimus Prime.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.66,0:18:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Optimus!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.46,0:18:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have The Forge.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.96,0:18:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can use it to repair yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.56,0:18:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is not the reason I had you retrieve the relic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.86,0:19:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.56,0:19:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The power of the Forge is not unlimited.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.26,0:19:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Its energy has already begun to ebb.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.36,0:19:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's running low, who cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.46,0:19:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All we need is enough juice to get you back into fighting shape!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.96,0:19:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever power remains must be used to rebuild the Omega lock,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.46,0:19:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to restore Cybertron.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.86,0:19:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that would mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.46,0:19:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fate of all our kind is more vital... than that of any one of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.76,0:19:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... Including me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.86,0:19:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must do everything in our power to ensure Megatron's downfall,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.06,0:20:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but we will need to be smart about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.26,0:20:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, who put shoulderpads in command?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.16,0:20:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Temporary command.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.66,0:20:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ultra Magnus is the only logical choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.36,0:20:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was trained by Optimus
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.06,0:20:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and served as his commanding officer throughout the War For Cybertron.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.86,0:20:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, unless there is any further objection,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.66,0:20:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,soldier, please, follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.56,0:20:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye aye, Cap'n.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.66,0:20:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Autobots.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.36,0:20:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take your pick.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.96,0:20:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you're speaking my language,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.36,0:20:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.46,0:20:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Optimus, the Forge is a relic of the Primes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.06,0:20:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't use it to restore Cybertron, not without a Prime. Not without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.46,0:21:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There will be a new Prime.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.66,0:21:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can worry about that after we get you patched up, and we take down Megatron.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.56,0:21:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time for a new leader is upon us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.26,0:21:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In my spark...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.46,0:21:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that leader... stands before me right now.
